// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// ECOFUNDRIVE V2.0 - CATEGORY INDEX: BEACHES (EN)
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import ContentSection from '../../components/ContentSection.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
import Schemas from '../../components/Schemas.astro';

import { filterByCategory, getCategorySlug } from '../../lib/keywords';

const lang = 'en';
const category = 'beach';
const categorySlug = getCategorySlug(category, lang);

const beaches = filterByCategory(lang, category);
const sortedBeaches = beaches.sort((a, b) => {
  if (a.authority !== b.authority) return b.authority ? 1 : -1;
  return a.location.localeCompare(b.location);
});

const breadcrumbs = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Beaches' }
];
---

<PageLayout
  title="Best Beaches French Riviera | Complete Guide"
  metaTitle="Private Beaches & Beach Clubs French Riviera | Monaco, Nice, Cannes"
  metaDescription="Discover the most beautiful beaches on the French Riviera. Complete guide to private beaches, beach clubs and secret coves in Monaco, Nice, Cannes, Saint-Tropez, Antibes."
  lang={lang}
  canonical={`${siteConfig.siteUrl}/en/${categorySlug}`}
>
  <Hero
    title="French Riviera Beaches"
    subtitle={`Discover ${sortedBeaches.length} exceptional beaches on the French Riviera. Complete guide by David Chemla, Google Local Guide Level 6.`}
    image="/images/hero/shared/homepage-riviera-1920w.webp"
  />

  <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbs} lang={lang} />

  <ContentSection alignment="center">
    <h2>Best Beaches Guide</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      Legendary beach clubs, luxury private beaches and secret coves. 
      Discover our selection of the most beautiful beaches on the French Riviera, from Monaco to Saint-Tropez.
    </p>
  </ContentSection>

  <ContentSection>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
      {sortedBeaches.map((beach) => (
        <a 
          href={`/${beach.language}/${beach.keyword}`}
          class="category-card"
        >
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: {beach.mode === 'B' ? 'var(--accent)' : 'var(--accent-blue)'}; color: white; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600;">
              {beach.mode === 'B' ? 'VTC BOOKING' : 'GUIDE'}
            </span>
            {beach.authority && (
              <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #FFD700;" title="Authority page">‚≠ê</span>
            )}
          </div>
          
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.3;">
            {beach.keyword.replace(/-/g, ' ').replace(/\b\w/g, l => l.toUpperCase())}
          </h3>
          
          <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; flex-grow: 1;">
            üìç {beach.location}
          </p>
          
          <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">
            Learn more ‚Üí
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </ContentSection>

  <CTA
    title="VTC transfer to beaches"
    subtitle="Premium shuttle service to all beach clubs and private beaches on the French Riviera."
    location="end"
    lang={lang}
  />

  <Schemas
    type="collection"
    data={{
      items: sortedBeaches,
      title: "Best Beaches French Riviera | Complete Guide",
      description: "Discover the most beautiful beaches on the French Riviera. Complete guide to private beaches and beach clubs.",
      url: `${siteConfig.siteUrl}/en/${categorySlug}`
    }}
  />

  <Schemas type="organization" />

  <Schemas
    type="breadcrumb"
    data={{ breadcrumbs }}
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .category-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .category-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
</style>
